    "To assess the performance of the complete ROM model, the reconstructed energy over the prediction horizon is calculated using an ensemble over 50 evenly-spaced windows in the test data.",
    "The results shown in Fig. 8a indicate a better reconstruction ability for models using d = 20, as expected due to the less restrictive autoencoder bottleneck.",
